        <sect1>
            <title>Amberry</title>

            <para>
                <e>Amberry is a town of some 1,200 people on the eastern bank of the
                <qv uri="kyle-river">Kyle River</qv>. It is an important market town
                for the farmlands hereabout, and also acts as a toll for road and
                river traffic not destined for the town itself.
            </para>
